{"tid":2157181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透：以色列5G建設將排除中国","createTime":"2020-08-15T00:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T10:05:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fcaf7c0a690de8072f63d11b2178034d96be15dc","tid":2157181,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"外電引述美國官員指，以色列將與美國達成協議，承諾在5G網路建設中不使用中國的技術。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一名不具名美國官員表示，美國樂觀地認為，以色列將決定只允許可信任的設備商加入5G網路建設，雙方可能在未來數星期內簽署諒解備忘錄。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，在過去一年多來，美國不斷說服盟友不要使用中國華為的5G技術與設備。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/chi/1846768</code></pre>"},{"pid":"887a4eddf0b5f378006c7fcb35cf30224a011335","tid":2157181,"uid":60924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:09:16.000Z","msg":"咁阿聯酋都應該跟風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a35e38f9f845e7fd9ebad5b80482b920aa8e601","tid":2157181,"uid":132898,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"Ericsson同Nokia表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99f4c4cf0e7256993ae7bd66ac20790dac35f58","tid":2157181,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"支持以色列打柒巴勒狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87194b2cbdc5f691a0322772dae239b193a27f0d","tid":2157181,"uid":187232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"以色列佬精甩尾，情報網世界第一<br />\n會用華為，除非滅國啦"},{"pid":"01aa366c28837d848939cc8e35ae0127b4af8ba9","tid":2157181,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a35e38f9f845e7fd9ebad5b80482b920aa8e601","tid":2157181,"uid":132898,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"Ericsson同Nokia表示<im